text: Arje Nadbornik (7 October 1935 - 5 July 2008) was a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman +97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
